================================================================================

This project uses the following third-party libraries:

1. Mem0 (https://github.com/mem0ai/mem0)
   - Memory system framework

2. OpenAI Python SDK
   - LLM integration

3. Qdrant Client
   - Vector database client

4. FastAPI
   - Web framework for webhook server

5. APScheduler
   - Scheduling framework

Concepts and inspirations:
- Microsoft TinyTroupe: Persona consistency framework
- Stanford Generative Agents: Reflection mechanism design

For complete dependency list, see pyproject.toml.
